            "angle": 0,
            "content": "Problem 5. Suppose the difference scheme \\( u^{n + 1} = Bu^n \\) is stable, and \\( C(\\Delta t) \\) is a bounded family of operators. Show that the scheme"
        },
        {
            "type": "equation",
            "bbox": [
                0.379,
                0.131,
                0.56,
                0.15
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "\\[\nu ^ {n + 1} = (B + \\Delta t C (\\Delta t)) u ^ {n}\n\\]"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.113,
                0.171,
                0.182,
                0.186
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "is stable."
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.112,
                0.206,
                0.827,
                0.298
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "Solution: Suppose \\( \\| B^k \\| \\leq K_1 \\) for \\( 0 \\leq k \\leq n \\) and \\( \\| C(\\Delta t) \\| \\leq K_2 \\). It suffices to show \\( (B + \\Delta t C(\\Delta t))^n \\) is bounded for \\( n\\Delta t \\leq T \\). This will consist of \\( 2^n \\) terms, of which \\( \\binom{n}{j} \\) terms involve \\( j \\) factors \\( \\Delta t C \\) interspersed in \\( n - j \\) factors \\( B \\); the latter can occur in at most \\( j + 1 \\) sequences of consecutive factors, the norm of each sequence being bounded by \\( K_1 \\), and hence the norm of each such term by \\( K_2^j K_1^{j+1} \\). Thus overall we obtain the bound"
        },
        {
            "type": "equation",
            "bbox": [
                0.32,
                0.305,
                0.618,
                0.385
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "\\[\n\\begin{array}{l} \\| \\bigl(B + \\Delta tC(\\Delta t)\\bigr)^{n}\\| \\leq \\sum_{j = 0}^{n}\\left( \\begin{array}{c}n\\\\ j \\end{array} \\right)K_{1}^{j + 1}(\\Delta tK_{2})^{j} \\\\ = K _ {1} \\left(1 + \\Delta t K _ {1} K _ {2}\\right) ^ {n} \\\\ \\leq K _ {1} e ^ {n \\Delta t K _ {1} K _ {2}} \\\\ \\end{array}\n\\]"
        },
