                0.427,
                0.827,
                0.462
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "Problem 6. Let \\( A \\) be an \\( m \\times m \\) nonsingular matrix. Suppose \\( \\inf_{p_n \\in P^n} ||p_n(A)|| = ||p^*(A)|| > 0 \\) where \\( P^n \\) denotes the set of all degree-\\( n \\) monic polynomials:"
        },
        {
            "type": "equation",
            "bbox": [
                0.256,
                0.481,
                0.68,
                0.5
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "\\[\nP ^ {n} = \\left\\{p: p \\text {i s a p o l y n o m i a l o f d e g r e e} n, p (z) = z ^ {n} + \\dots \\right\\}.\n\\]"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.113,
                0.52,
                0.285,
                0.537
