        {
            "type": "equation",
            "bbox": [
                0.382,
                0.588,
                0.556,
                0.605
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "\\[\n\\left\\| p _ {1} \\right\\| = \\left\\| p _ {2} \\right\\| = \\left\\| p \\right\\| = \\sigma_ {1},\n\\]"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.112,
                0.61,
                0.504,
                0.626
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "where \\(\\sigma_{1}\\) is the largest singular value. Let the SVD of \\(p\\) be"
        },
        {
            "type": "equation",
            "bbox": [
                0.37,
                0.636,
                0.567,
                0.652
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "\\[\np (A) = U \\operatorname {d i a g} \\left(\\sigma_ {1}, \\dots , \\sigma_ {n}\\right) V ^ {*}.\n\\]"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.112,
                0.663,
                0.743,
                0.679
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "Suppose \\(\\sigma_{1}\\) is \\(J\\)-fold, with left and right singular vectors \\(u_{1},\\ldots ,u_{J}\\) and \\(\\nu_{1},\\ldots ,\\nu_{J}\\), respectively."
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.113,
                0.687,
                0.361,
                0.701
