                0.297,
                0.71,
                0.641,
                0.74
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "\\[\n\\sigma_ {1} = \\| p (A) v _ {j} \\| \\leq \\frac {1}{2} \\left(\\| p _ {1} (A) v _ {j} \\| + \\| p _ {2} (A) v _ {j} \\|\\right) \\leq \\sigma_ {1},\n\\]"
