            "angle": 0,
            "content": "Construct \\( q \\in P^n \\) using \\( p_1 - p_2 \\) so that \\( q\\nu_j = 0 \\) and \\( q^* u_j = 0 \\). For a fixed \\( \\epsilon \\in (0,1) \\), define"
