            "bbox": [
                0.27,
                0.911,
                0.667,
                0.93
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "\\[\np _ {\\epsilon} ^ {*} p _ {\\epsilon} v _ {j} = (1 - \\epsilon) p _ {\\epsilon} ^ {*} p (A) v _ {j} = (1 - \\epsilon) \\sigma_ {1} p _ {\\epsilon} ^ {*} u _ {j} = (1 - \\epsilon) ^ {2} \\sigma_ {1} ^ {2} v _ {j}.\n\\]"
